
'''* Book: Reflections. By José María Arizmendiarrieta. Solidarity Hall with The Interpreters’ Cooperative of Madison, 2020'''

URL = https://solidarityhall.org/in_action/arizmendi-reflections-translation/

=Description=

"Solidarity Hall’s current publishing project, a collaboration with The Interpreters’ Cooperative of Madison, is a new translation of the Reflections of Mondragon Cooperatives founder Fr. José María Arizmendiarrieta, known also simply as Arizmendi. Compiled by Joxe Azurmendi and first published, in 1999, as Pensamientos in Spanish and Basque, this small work is a book that “belongs in the back pocket of aspiring cooperators,” as Nathan Schneider has recently put it. We aim to place it there — a fresh edition in the hands of an emerging cooperative generation."
(https://solidarityhall.org/in_action/arizmendi-reflections-translation/)